Property.name: DateOfBirth
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the person's date of birth. </summary>

Property.name: DvaNumber
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the DVA file number on the person's repatriation health card. </summary>

Property.name: FamilyName
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the family name that appears on the person's Medicare or DVA card. </summary>

Property.name: GivenName
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the given name that appears on the person's Medicare or DVA card. </summary>

Property.name: MedicareIrn
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the 1-digit IRN for this person on the Medicare card. </summary>

Property.name: MedicareNumber
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the 10-digit card number on the person's Medicare card. </summary>

Property.name: Sex
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the person's sex. </summary>
